<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_372_r1l18">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Peter Lucʒ vnd C </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l19"><expan>vvircʒburg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> . vvie ſıe ewr dyener hanman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l20">von Rynheim von ſölcher <expan>vngeuerlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geſchiht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l21">wegen als ſich <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> de </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dienern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l22">vnd den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>hieob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> im lande <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l23"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in ein Sloſʒ daern bey der laen gelegen . cʒeſtellen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l24">gemant hab . Als das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden dy <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l25">ſelber auch wol ercʒelen werden . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr Jn durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dinſte wıllen darynne ewr gnade beweiſen vvollet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l27">daʒ ſie ſolcher vngeuerlıkeit genyſſen vnd ledig vverden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l28">Als etc das wöllen etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthoni . </ab>
</div>
